    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You bolster the resolve of an injured ally.</p><p> As a Bonus Action, select one allied creature within 30 feet of you that has taken damage this initiative.</p><p> When you do, you spend one Superiority Die to inspire them.</p><p> They can choose to spend one of their own Hit die.</p><p> Regardless, they regain hit points equal to twice your Superiority Die plus their Hit die if they spent one.</p><p></p>",
